{"tid":95932,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲覺得自己好廢","createTime":"2017-01-26T11:59:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T16:50:39.000Z","uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59f0a990f7d54888320a86a46bdaa17ec96e98cf","tid":95932,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"讀書又唔係好過人（asso仔)<br />\n工作方面 <br />\n其實一路都覺得自己工作態度有問題<br />\n多數返完份pt三個月就唔想做 <br />\n之前返過u記同補習<br />\n我又唔係怕辛苦 其實係覺得好攰 唔係自己性格  返補習完全覺得自己係誤人子弟<br />\n到辭工個陣又唔夠膽正面講 唯有遲到射波做藉口 博辭<br />\n其實我一路都知咁樣做人好無責任感好仆街 一路都好自責  呢種性格好不要得 有咩淨係去避 唔會去解決 <br />\n除此之外 自己又無樣叻 永遠做乜都半桶水<br />\n唔識堅持 <br />\n我真係覺得自己好廢 無撚用 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffb2e5c96413282afaa367fe1f651a104e15974","tid":95932,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:00:37.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n覺得自己好似冇野叻過人咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但我仲信天生我才必有用嘅 只係未搵到啫 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"8fac1cb9a79e1e61691006866f93e68c36a3ad96","tid":95932,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺<br />\n覺得自己好似冇野叻過人咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但我仲信天生我才必有用嘅 只係未搵到啫 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\n一嚟覺得自己無用二嚟覺得我自己個態度好有問題但又唔去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bc8193c53865bfd4b2aebb4083a22cb7bab774","tid":95932,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺<br />\n覺得自己好似冇野叻過人咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">但我仲信天生我才必有用嘅 只係未搵到啫 好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></blockquote><br />\n一嚟覺得自己無用二嚟覺得我自己個態度好有問題但又唔去改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做咩唔改呀？<br />\n係咪有咩困難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c0e516b33efecef3807ddda1bc1ebd02c10af0","tid":95932,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:40:13.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"c96aca4812b86299de8d0cf89b4089b9323c08f6","tid":95932,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T12:41:54.000Z","msg":"醜樣<br />\n又蠢<br />\n體質差<br />\n性格又怪 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  周不時都好討厭自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b04cee76bd766cfdc28044c04a0b5b6aa8cdbea","tid":95932,"uid":4998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醜樣<br />\n又蠢<br />\n體質差<br />\n性格又怪 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  周不時都好討厭自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8599e4df46ef52eaf21e30c67142d0a15a2376a9","tid":95932,"uid":14888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:18:50.000Z","msg":"同你情況一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f45cfa0770688c7b8c27d9b46a95a02522cbca","tid":95932,"uid":49250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T16:39:31.000Z","msg":"有時想自殺 但可惜屋企住得唔高"},{"pid":"4837ae10c44fb8ddb4bcd9d